➜『千家风采』贾香雅绝句十首
http://www.sohu.com/a/416567008_753274	9029
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200905/066f8a0aa18744d3b14c414a9cea83e7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>千家档案</p>
<p>贾香雅，女，笔名风舒，诗词爱好者，有作品录于《千家诗词》和《百狼图》。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>远行人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万里步霜尘，冥冥自有因。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相逢何必问，风雪远行人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>拜山</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">千山云外行，冷暖自相迎。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但见风行处，缘来是此声。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>云海归来无梦生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远树含烟数鸟声，红尘到此隔千城。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">行行飘袂任谁去，云海归来无梦生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>岭外行云天地宽（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">岭外行云天地宽，浮生留白始能闲。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">枯崖老柏通今古，解语婆娑草木间。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>古寺前</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">万里烟尘不欲留，满身风雨何曾休？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">青袍吹起千堆雪，似把前尘化水流。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>拜佛</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">沧海恒沙合十数，俯身参尽风霜苦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">淡将明月洗前尘，万水千山皆净土。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>药泉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一瓢明月映三身，一饮清风洗客尘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再去人间无挂碍，万千悲喜化为春。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>转山</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">元知生死有千关，且过禅林天外天。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">听雪听风皆自在，转山转水转尘缘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诵经</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">高山转眼瘦成沙，一字恒沙一妙华。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">若得此间真实意，菩提无籽亦开花。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>感</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红尘来去几千身，且悟且行且忘尘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">岭上参听风与雪，云中焉有不归人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>感（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">浮生如水亦如埃，相遇若萍孰可猜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天地苍茫无止境，清风不老故人怀。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>悟</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平生阅尽是沧桑，终落碑前字几行。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不与烟花争绚烂，只和流水共天长。</p>
<h1>《千家诗词》</h1>
<p>主编：郑万才</p>
<p>副主编：王惠玲、王天明、胡晓娜</p>
<p>编辑：胡敏、刘宴会、杨余龙、刘爱红、韦化彪</p>
<p>版权说明：《千家诗词》所发诗词，皆为作者授权</p>
➜【诗家自选】孙艳梅绝句选
http://www.sohu.com/a/416648900_753274	48679
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200905/c66e8a8648e84f9b8d700c8dd13943dc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>孙艳梅，女，河北唐山人，大学学历，诗词爱好者。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>小草</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">难入芝兰室，荒原自在生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽无蜂蝶绕，昂首亦峥嵘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>早春</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">冰融万物苏，点翠近观无。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还待多情雨，来描五彩图。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>咏竹（新韵</strong>）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">几载起毫厘，扎根固肇基。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只期淋润雨，飞长向天齐。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>理行囊</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">整饬行囊满，还疑少一宗。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">非为衣食用，是母眷儿浓。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>立夏（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">斗柄转东南，风和去厚衫。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">春播千粒粟，葱郁漫晴川。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>荷塘</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">翠盖银珠耀，红香菡萏开。</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
